096-116b @#/ /bad kan gyi nad sel ba'i gzungs sngags/ /'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo/ /oM shAn+ti shAn+ti/ b+hi ti shAn+ti/ sarba bi ti mu la mya ga sa swA hA/ zas ma zhu ba dang / /spos pa dang / skran nad dang / chud pa khrag skyugs pa dang / bad kan gyi zug gzer rab tu sel lo/ /bad kan gyi nad sel ba'i gzungs rdzogs so/
